{"tid":2340223,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲咩感情台嘅po你要長期置頂?","createTime":"2020-12-25T09:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T19:58:35.000Z","uid":327979,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"45a0211ff3f09ea5ede5e8d07cb8f09ce8a75ec9","tid":2340223,"uid":327979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:37:14.000Z","msg":"如果啱啱俾人飛，想復合既，千祈唔好lur地！男女都係！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/839259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/839259</a><br />\n<br />\n利申 啱啱分手 每一日都會諗關於男女關係嘅事<br />\n呢個po係每一次 自己亂諗野嘅時候都會去睇一睇<br />\n每次睇完都會覺得舒服咗好多 雖然知道有啲道理嘅事係人都明<br />\n但唔係個個都做到 每一次睇呢個po都會提點到自己 要去做好自己<br />\n歡迎拋磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝 各位巴絲聖誕快樂"},{"pid":"0d9c1af0520ed6136893c282c1979f5aaa1c7cd8","tid":2340223,"uid":327340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"善意打破0回覆<br />\n聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0166275e3e119bffc349152ff26f694b06b36934","tid":2340223,"uid":242311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:19:01.000Z","msg":"呢個po我都睇咗好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3988332ea474c51a72574df771a6dd00afdc938","tid":2340223,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:19:08.000Z","msg":"哈 又一pair分手 開心～"},{"pid":"ac7432bc1557726f8f94f03c875febdd02a86b49","tid":2340223,"uid":327979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d9c1af0520ed6136893c282c1979f5aaa1c7cd8","tid":2340223,"uid":327340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"善意打破0回覆<br />\n聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T19:58:35.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}